---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" showSearch={false}>
  <div class="container page-content">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About nex</h1>
      <p class="lead">Building the future of developer tool management.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Nex was born from a simple idea: developers shouldn't spend hours configuring their environment. 
        We believe that sharing and using developer tools should be as easy as installing a mobile app.
        Our mission is to create a universal package manager that simplifies the distribution and usage of CLI tools across all platforms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>The Story</h2>
      <p>
        Started in 2023, Nex began as a small script to manage dotfiles and local scripts. 
        It quickly evolved into a full-fledged package manager when we realized the need for a 
        lightweight, cross-platform solution that doesn't require complex dependencies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Team & Contributors</h2>
      <p>
        Nex is an open-source project driven by a community of passionate developers.
        We welcome contributions from everyone, whether it's code, documentation, or feedback.
      </p>
      
      <div class="contributors-link">
        <a href="https://github.com/devkiraa/nex/graphs/contributors" target="_blank" class="btn">
          View Contributors on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--nex-black);
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--nex-gray);
  }
  
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--nex-black);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }
  
  .section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--nex-dark);
  }
  
  .contributors-link {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--nex-red);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  
  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--nex-red-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>
